modName: Alex's Guardian Stones 50 percent XP - DELETED
summary: Makes the guardian stone level abilities 50% faster instead of 20%.
descriptionHtml:
[color=#ea9999]Details[/color]
Not much to say here.

With this mod, the guardian stones level abilities 50% faster instead of 20%.

[color=#ea9999]Installation[/color]
Use NMM or install manually. No scripts in here.

[color=#ea9999]Compatibility[/color]
Compatible with anything except mods that edit the guardian stone perks.
